So the REML estimate is correct:

dat <- structure(list(study = c("AA", "BB", "CC",
"EE", "DDD"), en = c(9, 41, 29, 8, 13
), em = c(32, 27.5, 28.7, 22.8, 30.5), esd = c(1.9, 3.8, 5.2,
